very cute park with blooming flowers and nice small trails.
Nice little parc, great in the summer for a little shade, picnic or even some tan time, also has two playgrounds for children.
Beautiful city square,  very well maintained garden with lovely children's play area.
Good place for kids. There are 2 tables for ping-pong, one table for chess, playground for kids to play with sand.
Small and nice place, you shouldn't come far distance to see it but if you're already around you can pass by.
Great place for families with children. My son had a lovely time in the play area and the fountain on the main green is really pretty too.

Small little park, though very beautiful and spacious, with lots of places to sit. Very clean and well maintained, perfect place to catch up with people, read a book enjoy some sun. Lot of people also run here. There is a children's play area, small shop inside and even clean toilets around the park. Very well situated and receives lots of sunshine.
Super parc with flowers vegetables and water fountain
Lovely little park with plenty of seats. Quite & relaxing. Good shaded areas as well as open.

Very chill park, lots of space and fun areas, local schoolchildren go there too. Since Its right across from the school "Camille See" you can hear the bell ring every hour, but it isn't an inconvenient

Nice park to walk around and there's playground for kids
Beautiful park with many different places to sit either in the sun or in the shade.   Also large spaces for children to play.  There is also a large pond.
Perfect for a summer evening, tranquil and beautiful.

An oasis in the middle of a very busy city. You can see the top of the Eiffel tower from there. Joggers, couples in love, moms with small children, and also a few drinks can be seen there too. A nice place to relax and just let Paris be Paris.
Breathtaking park (particularly in the summer)! Beautiful flowers & fountain, along with grass to sit and an area to play soccer.
Nice and clean park.
Usually very crowded on sunny days but still a nice picnic spot
Very beautiful, green, spacious park with fountain and children playgrounds for different ages! And lots of seating options as well :)
This is one of the best parks in Paris!! Highly recommend coming here and having a picnic. WiFi is available, there are bathrooms and there is seating all around the park
A small park compared to many others in Paris but it's charming with a fountain, mature trees, flowering shrubs, benches to sit , children's  playground  & a snack kiosk in summer
Very quiet and clean. My wife and I enjoyed the relaxing moment here. We felt like we could invest an hour a day to be here together.
The park is really big and cozy, big enough yo do the picnic lots of events are there
A realky nice square and park in Paris. Seems great on a lovely day. Nice grass area, and playgrounds for children.
